params.sqlcmd: "select " +" T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK.\\"ITEM_CD\\" as \\"ITEM_CD\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"ITEM_NAME\\" as \\"ITEM_NAME\\", " +" T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK.\\"JOB_ODR_CD\\" as \\"JOB_ODR_CD\\", " +" T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK.\\"JOB_ODR_DETAIL_NO\\" as \\"JOB_ODR_DETAIL_NO\\", " +" T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK.\\"WH_CD\\" as \\"WH_CD\\", " +" M_WH.\\"WH_NAME\\" as \\"WH_NAME\\", " +" M_WH.\\"MRP_FLG\\" as \\"MRP_FLG\\", " +" TO_CHAR(T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK.\\"STOCK_ON_HAND_QTY\\", 'fm999999999999999990.0999') as \\"STOCK_ON_HAND_QTY\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"DRAW_CD\\" as \\"DRAW_CD\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"SPEC\\" as \\"SPEC\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"STOCK_UNIT\\" as \\"STOCK_UNIT\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"UNIT_QTY_TYP\\" as \\"UNIT_QTY_TYP\\" " +"from " +" T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK, " +" M_ITEM, " +" M_WH " +"where " +" T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK.ITEM_CD = M_ITEM.ITEM_CD(+) " +" and T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK.WH_CD = M_WH.WH_CD(+) " +" and T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK.\\"ITEM_CD\\" like ? " +" and T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK.\\"JOB_ODR_CD\\" like ? " +" and T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK.\\"WH_CD\\" like ? " +" and T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +"order by " +" ITEM_CD, " +" JOB_ODR_CD, " +" WH_CD"

"select " +" TO_CHAR(SUM(T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK.\\"STOCK_ON_HAND_QTY\\"), 'TM9') as \\"SUM_STOCK_ON_HAND_QTY\\" " +"from " +" T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK, " +" M_WH " +"where " +" T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK.\\"WH_CD\\" = M_WH.\\"WH_CD\\" " +" and M_WH.\\"MRP_FLG\\" = 1 " +" and T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" and T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK.\\"JOB_ODR_CD\\" = ? " +" and T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ?"

"SELECT " +" PLANT_CD " +"FROM " +" T_OD " +"WHERE " +" PLANT_CD = ? " +" AND ITEM_CD = ? " +" AND JOB_ODR_CD = ? " +" AND JOB_ODR_DETAIL_NO = ? " +" AND PARENT_OD_NO IS NOT NULL " +" AND DM_STS_TYP <> 9"

"select " +" count(1) " +"from " +" T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK, " +" M_ITEM, " +" M_WH " +"where " +" T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK.ITEM_CD = M_ITEM.ITEM_CD(+) " +" and T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK.WH_CD = M_WH.WH_CD(+) " +" and T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK.\\"ITEM_CD\\" like ? " +" and T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK.\\"JOB_ODR_CD\\" like ? " +" and T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK.\\"WH_CD\\" like ? " +" and T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +" and ROWNUM <= TO_NUMBER(?) + 1"
